ose weapons\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1772}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1807}, {\"ngram\": \"the Lord\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are in a spiritual battle, and the best thing in this spiritual battle is to gain ground, not just hold ground.\\\"\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1968, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a spiritual battle\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"the best thing\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"this spiritual battle\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"ground\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"ground\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ANALYSIS: 'The Chosen' Tackles Olympic Blasphemy with Viral Pic of 'Authentic' Last Supper Laurie shared his comments while also discussing the powerful \\\"Jesus Revolution\\\" baptism his church recently held at Pirates Cove in California, a historic beach where baptisms have routinely unfolded.\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 2265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2197, \"end\": 2207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 1.318909988094709e-13, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ANALYSIS\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"The Chosen' Tackles Olympic Blasphemy\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2018}, {\"ngram\": \"Viral Pic\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"Authentic\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"Last Supper Laurie\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2067}, {\"ngram\": \"his comments\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2087}, {\"ngram\": \"the powerful \\\"Jesus Revolution\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2140}, {\"ngram\": \"baptism\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2149}, {\"ngram\": \"his church\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2160}, {\"ngram\": \"Pirates Cove\", \"